'''紅髮'''是一種1%至2%的人口擁有的[[髮色|髮色]]，顏色屬於紅色系或橙色系，包括酒紅色、棕紅色、亮銅色和紅橙色。 

==人口分佈==
據統計，目前大約有1%至2%的人口擁有紅髮<ref name="redalert">[http://www.washingtonpost.com/ac2/wp-dyn?pagename=article&node=&contentId=A47332-2002Mar18&notFound=true Red Alert!] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20120527073213/www.washingtonpost.com/ac2/wp-dyn?pagename=article&node=&contentId=A47332-2002Mar18&notFound=true |date=2012-05-27 }} Washington Post: Original Date 2002-03-19. Accessed 2007-02-06.</ref><ref>[[National_Geographic|National Geographic]], September, 2007</ref>。紅髮最常出現於歐洲[[北欧|北部]]和[[西欧|西部]]。 

===歐洲===
[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]平均每人的紅髮人數量是世界上最高的，紅髮人約佔全國人口的10%。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Moffat|first1=Alistair|last2=Wilson|first2=James|title=The Scots: A Genetic Journey|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=zdm8BQAAQBAJ&q=the+scots:+a+genetic+journey|access-date=6 June 2016|isbn=9780857900203|date=2011-05-01|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017051936/https://books.google.com/books?id=zdm8BQAAQBAJ&q=the+scots:+a+genetic+journey|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

[[大不列颠岛|大不列颠岛]]的紅髮人比例也相當高。[[苏格兰|苏格兰]]的紅髮人佔全國人口的6%，其中全世界最密集的紅髮人地區為[[爱丁堡|爱丁堡]]，是世界的紅髮首都。<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.heraldscotland.com/news/13157439.auld-reekie-is-world-capital-for-ginger-hair/ | title=Auld Reekie is world capital for ginger hair | access-date=2021-10-17 | archive-date=2021-03-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308072734/https://www.heraldscotland.com/news/13157439.auld-reekie-is-world-capital-for-ginger-hair/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="telegraph.co.uk">{{cite news|last=Cramb|first=Auslan|title=Edinburgh is surprise capital of redheaded Britain and Ireland|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/science/10264427/Edinburgh-is-surprise-capital-of-redheaded-Britain-and-Ireland.html|access-date=21 April 2017|work=The Telegraph|date=24 August 2013|archive-date=2021-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019204455/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/science/10264427/Edinburgh-is-surprise-capital-of-redheaded-Britain-and-Ireland.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

紅髮也出現在[[阿什肯纳兹犹太人|阿什肯纳兹犹太人]]群中。<ref>{{cite book |author=Abel, Ernest L. |title=Jewish genetic disorders: a layman's guide |publisher=McFarland |location=Jefferson, N.C |year=2001 |page=[https://archive.org/details/jewishgeneticdis00erne/page/229 229] |isbn=978-0-7864-0941-9 |url=https://archive.org/details/jewishgeneticdis00erne/page/229 }}</ref>1903年，5.6%的波蘭猶太人有紅髮。<ref>''Elkind. Evrei Trudi Antropologitshes-kavo Amdilla, xxi.'', Moscow, 1903</ref>其他研究發現全體猶太女人中有3.69%擁有紅髮，但大約10.9%的猶太男人有紅[[胡须|胡须]]。<ref>Maurice Fishberg (1911). Jews, race & environment. 99. Transaction Publishers. {{ISBN|978-1-4128-0574-2}}</ref>20世紀前的歐洲文化中，紅髮被視為一個猶太人的刻板特徵：[[西班牙宗教裁判所|西班牙宗教裁判所]]活動期間，所有紅髮人都被認為是猶太人。<ref name="European Imagination 2010">''The Jewish Persona in the European Imagination: A Case of Russian Literature'', By Leonid Livak, (Stanford University Press 2010).</ref> 

===亞洲===
在亞洲中，紅髮出現於部分[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]人、<ref>{{Cite book|last1=Wahab|first1=Shaista|url=|title=A Brief History of Afghanistan|last2=Youngerman|first2=Barry|date=2007|publisher=Infobase Publishing|isbn=978-1-4381-0819-3|language=en|quote=northeast of Kabul, however, the local population includes many people with blond or red hair and blue or ...}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last1=Studies|first1=American University (Washington, D. C. ) Foreign Area|url=|title=Area Handbook for Afghanistan|last2=Smith|first2=Harvey Henry|date=1969|publisher=U.S. Government Printing Office|language=en|quote=They are generally of medium , slender physique , with dark , sometimes red , hair}}</ref>[[阿拉伯人|阿拉伯人]]、[[伊朗人|伊朗人]]、[[蒙古族|蒙古族]]人、[[突厥语族群|突厥人]]、[[苗族|苗族]]人和[[苗族蒙人|苗族蒙人]]。 

== 生物化學和基因學 ==
紅髮的顏色源自毛髮中的[[假黑色素|假黑色素]]。紅髮的假黑色素遠高於它的真黑色素。紅髮人的[[16号染色体|16号染色体]]有兩個[[隱性基因|隱性基因]]，這會使[[黑素皮質素受體1|黑素皮質素受體1]]蛋白發生轉變。由於皮膚和眼睛也有相同的基因，紅髮人常有白皙的皮膚和雀斑，也對[[紫外線|紫外線]]較為敏感。 

== 动物 ==
除了人類外，紅色毛髮也可見於其他[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]，比如[[紅毛猩猩|紅毛猩猩]]、[[松鼠|松鼠]]、[[山羊|山羊]]，或是出產於蘇格蘭的[[高地牛|高地牛]]。某些狗或貓的品種，以及部分[[狐狸|狐狸]]和[[鹿|鹿]]，也擁有紅毛。 

